<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko" class="h-100">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <script src="/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        .row {
            display: flex;
        }

        .sep {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .sepText {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .sepText::before,
        .sepText::after {
            content: '';
            flex: 1;
            width: 1px;
            background: currentColor;
            /* matches font color */
            margin: .25em;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="d-flex flex-column h-100">
    <%include ../header %>

        <!-- Begin page content -->
        <main role="main" class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="mt-5">아이디/비밀번호 찾기</h1>


                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-5">
                        <h2>아이디 찾기</h2>
                        <p>아이디 조차도 기억나지 않아, 해매시는 분들을 위해 아이디 찾기가 있습니다. 가입할 때 사용하던 이메일만 있으면 알려드립니다.</p>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="idfind">아이디 찾기</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-2 sep">
                        <span class="sepText">
                      또는
                  </span>

                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-5">
                        <h2>비밀번호 재설정</h2>
                        <p>비밀번호를 잊어버려서 곤란할 때, 아이디를 입력하면 가입할 때 입력했던 이메일로 임시 비밀번호를 보내드립니다.</p>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="pwfind">비밀번호 재설정</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </main>
        <script src="../javascripts/valid.js"></script>
        <script>
            $("#idfind").click(function() {
               location.href="/users/idfind" ;
            });
            $("#pwfind").click(function() {
               location.href="/users/pwfind" ;
            });
        </script>
        <%include ../footer %>
</body>

</html>
